I will think about your cooking every day.

593
00:28:23,620 --> 00:28:24,730
I will come back

594
00:28:25,220 --> 00:28:26,480
every annual holiday.

595
00:28:26,660 --> 00:28:27,340
Forget it.

596
00:28:28,270 --> 00:28:29,270
Even if you agree,

597
00:28:29,760 --> 00:28:31,420
your girlfriend won't agree.

598
00:28:31,860 --> 00:28:33,460
You have only a few holidays.

599
00:28:33,480 --> 00:28:34,350
You'd better stay at home

600
00:28:34,350 --> 00:28:36,010
and keep your family company.

601
00:28:37,750 --> 00:28:38,860
She's my wife now.

602
00:28:40,170 --> 00:28:40,680
So soon?

603
00:28:43,450 --> 00:28:44,430
We got the marriage certificate.

604
00:28:44,430 --> 00:28:46,610
But I don't have time to hold a wedding ceremony yet.

605
00:28:46,610 --> 00:28:48,020
Maybe next year.

606
00:28:49,270 --> 00:28:50,540
I have some missions going on

607
00:28:50,540 --> 00:28:52,340
until the next Spring Festival.

608
00:28:52,460 --> 00:28:53,820
We'll celebrate the Spring Festival first.

609
00:28:53,820 --> 00:28:55,280
And after she gives birth,

610
00:28:55,380 --> 00:28:56,580
she needs to recover.

611
00:28:57,190 --> 00:28:58,610
It'll be the year after next year.

612
00:28:58,610 --> 00:29:00,630
It's too cold to get married in winter.

613
00:29:00,630 --> 00:29:01,890
She loves to be pretty.

614
00:29:01,970 --> 00:29:02,810
I don't want her

615
00:29:02,810 --> 00:29:04,200
to wear a wedding dress

616
00:29:04,230 --> 00:29:05,160
in cold weather.

617
00:29:05,900 --> 00:29:06,580
Wait, wait.

618
00:29:07,500 --> 00:29:08,430
What did you say?

619
00:29:08,830 --> 00:29:10,230
You even have a child now?

620
00:29:10,970 --> 00:29:12,580
This is double happiness.

621
00:29:14,530 --> 00:29:15,450
Indeed.

622
00:29:17,520 --> 00:29:18,690
But today,

623
00:29:19,560 --> 00:29:21,430
please don't share the news with them.

624
00:29:21,430 --> 00:29:23,020
I don't want to celebrate today.

625
00:29:23,020 --> 00:29:23,820
I understand.

626
00:29:26,520 --> 00:29:28,720
Everyone has their moment of weakness.

627
00:29:30,270 --> 00:29:30,910
Zhong.

628
00:29:31,420 --> 00:29:32,380
Can you do it?

629
00:29:32,400 --> 00:29:33,990
Look how timid you are.

630
00:29:34,090 --> 00:29:35,350
Let me do it.
I can do it.

631
00:29:35,660 --> 00:29:36,460
There's no need for you to help.

632
00:29:36,460 --> 00:29:37,440
Please be seated.

633
00:29:37,440 --> 00:29:38,060
Let me do it.

634
00:29:38,060 --> 00:29:38,940
How can we let you do it?

635
00:29:38,940 --> 00:29:39,740
We're the youngsters.

636
00:29:39,740 --> 00:29:40,320
That's right.

637
00:29:40,320 --> 00:29:40,790
Yeah.

638
00:29:40,820 --> 00:29:42,090
He thinks we're good for nothing.

639
00:29:42,090 --> 00:29:43,050
Let me tell you.

640
00:29:43,310 --> 00:29:44,940
You can have a good meal today.

641
00:29:44,940 --> 00:29:45,940
My cooking skills

642
00:29:46,050 --> 00:29:47,050
are as good as Lu.

643
00:29:47,380 --> 00:29:48,810
Excuse me.

644
00:29:48,840 --> 00:29:49,520
Don't...

645
00:29:49,610 --> 00:29:50,370
Make way.

646
00:30:00,010 --> 00:30:02,610
Seeing Captain Lu reminds me of a lot of things.

647
00:30:03,610 --> 00:30:04,410
What is it?

648
00:30:05,260 --> 00:30:07,460
Only compliments are allowed tonight,

649
00:30:07,550 --> 00:30:09,010
no bad words to each other.

650
00:30:11,710 --> 00:30:12,910
Keep your voice down.

651
00:30:13,110 --> 00:30:14,040
Zhong is asleep.

652
00:30:15,270 --> 00:30:15,960
Captain Lu.

653
00:30:16,300 --> 00:30:16,840
You definitely

654
00:30:16,840 --> 00:30:18,440
never slept with him before.

655
00:30:18,580 --> 00:30:19,220
Back then,

656
00:30:19,220 --> 00:30:20,130
we played cards

657
00:30:20,130 --> 00:30:21,060
and watched movies.

658
00:30:21,060 --> 00:30:22,100
And he can still sleep.

659
00:30:22,100 --> 00:30:23,760
This volume can't wake him up.

660
00:30:24,690 --> 00:30:25,780
This is not the sensitivity

661
00:30:25,780 --> 00:30:26,840
a SWAT should have.

662
00:30:28,320 --> 00:30:29,160
However,

663
00:30:29,630 --> 00:30:30,880
when the phone rings,

664
00:30:31,330 --> 00:30:32,930
he will wake up immediately.

665
00:30:33,040 --> 00:30:33,890
No delay.

666
00:30:36,680 --> 00:30:37,520
I can testify.

667
00:30:37,990 --> 00:30:39,190
I have seen it before.

668
00:30:39,960 --> 00:30:40,820
He joined late.

669
00:30:41,220 --> 00:30:42,550
I didn't get to lead him.

670
00:30:42,980 --> 00:30:44,010
I have no idea

671
00:30:44,160 --> 00:30:45,690
about his sleeping habits.

672
00:30:46,900 --> 00:30:47,610
However,

673
00:30:48,450 --> 00:30:50,580
I was indeed unqualified previously.

674
00:30:51,860 --> 00:30:52,520
Captain Lu,

675
00:30:52,670 --> 00:30:53,960
you are good at everything.

676
00:30:53,960 --> 00:30:56,220
But there's one single thing that you are not good enough at.

677
00:30:56,220 --> 00:30:57,620
You like to self-reflect

678
00:30:57,630 --> 00:30:59,090
and put blame on yourself.

679
00:31:01,660 --> 00:31:02,770
I agree.

680
00:31:03,450 --> 00:31:05,980
The ancients self-reflect three times a day.

681
00:31:06,340 --> 00:31:09,140
You can reflect on yourself 17 to 18 times a day.

682
00:31:11,610 --> 00:31:12,060
Fine.

683
00:31:13,060 --> 00:31:13,790
I'll change.

684
00:31:17,480 --> 00:31:18,250
Listen.

685
00:31:18,530 --> 00:31:19,590
You have to change.

686
00:31:20,010 --> 00:31:21,470
Loosen up.

687
00:31:21,660 --> 00:31:23,320
You need to relax, Captain Lu.

688
00:31:24,490 --> 00:31:25,340
But

689
00:31:25,390 --> 00:31:26,780
his psychological quality

690
00:31:26,780 --> 00:31:27,710
is his weakness.

691
00:31:28,690 --> 00:31:30,570
He has to face the reality.

692
00:31:34,250 --> 00:31:35,450
Speaking of the past,

693
00:31:36,100 --> 00:31:37,060
let me tell you

694
00:31:37,580 --> 00:31:39,040
Captain Qin’s love story.

695
00:31:42,420 --> 00:31:43,550
Didn’t we just agree

696
00:31:43,580 --> 00:31:46,310
to not say anything bad about each other tonight?

697
00:31:46,470 --> 00:31:47,670
I'm not talking bad about you.

698
00:31:47,670 --> 00:31:49,140
I was going to talk about your first love.

699
00:31:49,140 --> 00:31:49,980
My first love?

700
00:31:51,270 --> 00:31:51,780
Who?

701
00:31:53,530 --> 00:31:55,000
You weren't here at that time.

702
00:31:55,000 --> 00:31:56,000
He just came here.

703
00:31:56,830 --> 00:31:59,330
A few female colleagues were sent by the brigade.

704
00:31:59,330 --> 00:32:00,320
He had a crush on

705
00:32:01,420 --> 00:32:02,220
one of them.

706
00:32:03,740 --> 00:32:04,500
Bullshit!

707
00:32:04,940 --> 00:32:05,910
Are you trying to deny it?

708
00:32:05,910 --> 00:32:06,580
That's not true.

709
00:32:06,580 --> 00:32:07,780
Why should I admit it?

710
00:32:08,050 --> 00:32:08,530
No.

711
00:32:08,900 --> 00:32:09,630
Captain Qin.

712
00:32:09,850 --> 00:32:10,540
Captain Lu

713
00:32:10,540 --> 00:32:12,320
has been talking to me all this while.

714
00:32:12,320 --> 00:32:13,450
Stop interrupting.

715
00:32:13,500 --> 00:32:14,140
In our squad,

716
00:32:14,140 --> 00:32:15,600
you are the most experienced in romance.

717
00:32:15,600 --> 00:32:16,860
Don't pretend to be innocent.

718
00:32:16,860 --> 00:32:17,990
I'm not pretending.

719
00:32:18,270 --> 00:32:19,220
He's talking nonsense.

720
00:32:19,220 --> 00:32:20,150
That's not true.

721
00:32:20,280 --> 00:32:21,540
That female colleague

722
00:32:21,770 --> 00:32:22,780
is capable,

723
00:32:22,810 --> 00:32:23,570
beautiful,

724
00:32:23,590 --> 00:32:24,450
and ambitious.

725
00:32:24,850 --> 00:32:26,130
Many people in our squad

726
00:32:26,130 --> 00:32:26,860
pursued her.

727
00:32:27,440 --> 00:32:28,680
I didn’t know

728
00:32:28,700 --> 00:32:30,560
Captain Qin would be interested.

729
00:32:30,590 --> 00:32:31,520
There's one time

730
00:32:32,110 --> 00:32:33,510
we're both in the office.

731
00:32:33,670 --> 00:32:34,450
That female colleague

732
00:32:34,450 --> 00:32:35,890
talked to me about work.

733
00:32:36,800 --> 00:32:37,110
No.

734
00:32:37,150 --> 00:32:38,310
When did it happen?

735
00:32:38,330 --> 00:32:39,470
Why don't I remember?

736
00:32:39,470 --> 00:32:40,240
And then?

737
00:32:40,780 --> 00:32:41,900
The story ends here.

738
00:32:41,900 --> 00:32:43,180
He left after that.

739
00:32:44,390 --> 00:32:45,530
How do you know

740
00:32:45,530 --> 00:32:47,190
Captain Qin had a crush on her?

741
00:32:47,350 --> 00:32:48,740
Lu Yanchen, don’t talk nonsense.

742
00:32:48,740 --> 00:32:49,620
After she left,

743
00:32:49,920 --> 00:32:51,300
I went behind Captain Qin

744
00:32:51,300 --> 00:32:51,700
to see

745
00:32:51,720 --> 00:32:53,450
the documents on his computer.

746
00:32:53,590 --> 00:32:54,470
I found that

747
00:32:55,570 --> 00:32:56,700
he was holding a bun,

748
00:32:57,340 --> 00:32:58,540
calm and cool,

749
00:32:58,620 --> 00:32:59,620
expressionless,

750
00:33:00,250 --> 00:33:01,310
using it as a mouse.

751
00:33:01,830 --> 00:33:02,580
Lu Yanchen.

752
00:33:03,960 --> 00:33:05,490
What are you talking about?

753
00:33:06,140 --> 00:33:07,580
It's way too obvious.

754
00:33:10,420 --> 00:33:11,460
No, that day,

755
00:33:13,020 --> 00:33:14,200
I wasn't feeling well.

756
00:33:14,200 --> 00:33:15,330
I took the wrong one.

757
00:33:17,940 --> 00:33:18,670
Captain Qin.

758
00:33:19,020 --> 00:33:20,760
It's not shameful to have a crush.

759
00:33:20,760 --> 00:33:21,710
You're a SWAT.

760
00:33:21,840 --> 00:33:24,020
Can't you distinguish a mouse and a bun?

761
00:33:24,020 --> 00:33:24,500
No.

762
00:33:24,500 --> 00:33:26,780
I was on night duty the night before.

763
00:33:27,130 --> 00:33:28,770
I wasn't in a good state.

764
00:33:29,260 --> 00:33:30,390
It seems Captain Qin

765
00:33:30,930 --> 00:33:32,510
wants more evidence and cases.

766
00:33:32,510 --> 00:33:32,980
Right?

767
00:33:37,720 --> 00:33:38,360
Fine.

768
00:33:39,460 --> 00:33:41,350
I did like her for a while.

769
00:33:41,660 --> 00:33:42,210
A while?

770
00:33:45,270 --> 00:33:47,110
Quite a while, okay?

771
00:33:48,970 --> 00:33:49,990
Tell me more.

772
00:33:52,940 --> 00:33:54,130
You have been pretending to sleep?

773
00:33:54,130 --> 00:33:54,710
No, Captain Qin.

774
00:33:54,710 --> 00:33:55,640
I didn't mean to.

775
00:33:56,150 --> 00:33:57,810
Captain Lu rarely comes back.

776
00:33:57,820 --> 00:33:59,510
I thought you two must want to have a chat.

777
00:33:59,510 --> 00:34:00,710
I don't want to sleep.

778
00:34:01,850 --> 00:34:03,310
Wang, it's all your fault.

779
00:34:03,740 --> 00:34:05,600
You insisted that I slept deeply.

780
00:34:05,670 --> 00:34:06,610
How can I open my eyes?

781
00:34:06,610 --> 00:34:07,250
Fine.

782
00:34:07,570 --> 00:34:08,590
Let me tell you one more.

783
00:34:08,590 --> 00:34:09,360
OK. OK.

784
00:34:09,400 --> 00:34:10,060
Lu Yanchen.

785
00:34:10,360 --> 00:34:11,159
You better...

786
00:34:22,280 --> 00:34:22,810
I still remember

787
00:34:22,810 --> 00:34:24,070
when we first moved in,

788
00:34:24,219 --> 00:34:25,620
we had cleaned this floor

789
00:34:25,679 --> 00:34:26,810
for quite some days.

790
00:34:29,239 --> 00:34:29,900
Yes.

791
00:34:30,570 --> 00:34:32,010
We painted the walls.

792
00:34:38,440 --> 00:34:39,010
Zhang,

793
00:34:39,889 --> 00:34:41,110
thank you

794
00:34:41,580 --> 00:34:42,219
for solving such a big problem

795
00:34:42,219 --> 00:34:43,500
for our brigade.

796
00:34:44,780 --> 00:34:46,310
My house is empty anyway.

797
00:34:46,469 --> 00:34:47,540
It's better to rent it to our people

798
00:34:47,540 --> 00:34:49,199
than renting it to outsiders.

799
00:34:49,350 --> 00:34:49,870
Look.

800
00:34:50,350 --> 00:34:51,540
It's really good

801
00:34:52,540 --> 00:34:53,739
after refurbishing.

802
00:34:58,620 --> 00:35:00,680
It's indeed lively to live together.

803
00:35:00,730 --> 00:35:01,490
However,

804
00:35:01,820 --> 00:35:02,880
everything is good

805
00:35:02,960 --> 00:35:03,540
but the lack of

806
00:35:03,540 --> 00:35:05,000
an independent bathroom.

807
00:35:07,020 --> 00:35:08,630
In the early years, the factory's dorm

808
00:35:08,630 --> 00:35:10,090
shared the same bathroom.

809
00:35:11,130 --> 00:35:12,260
The rent is cheap and

810
00:35:12,340 --> 00:35:13,600
it's close to the police force.

811
00:35:13,600 --> 00:35:14,830
That's more than enough.

812
00:35:14,830 --> 00:35:16,590
Sharing a bathroom is not a big deal.

813
00:35:16,590 --> 00:35:17,080
Yes.

814
00:35:18,000 --> 00:35:19,360
It's quite big inside.

815
00:35:19,400 --> 00:35:19,940
Besides,

816
00:35:19,940 --> 00:35:20,940
all the people who rent this house

817
00:35:20,940 --> 00:35:21,660
are all men.

818
00:35:21,950 --> 00:35:22,420
So,

819
00:35:22,420 --> 00:35:24,010
let's change it to a men's toilet.

820
00:35:24,010 --> 00:35:25,150
It'll be spacious enough for us.

821
00:35:25,150 --> 00:35:26,410
And it saves money too.

822
00:35:26,670 --> 00:35:27,630
Our base

823
00:35:27,660 --> 00:35:28,790
is far from the city.

824
00:35:28,960 --> 00:35:29,780
We can take care of each other

825
00:35:29,780 --> 00:35:31,190
by living together.

826
00:35:31,220 --> 00:35:31,820
It's good.

827
00:35:32,620 --> 00:35:33,730
When any of us get married,

828
00:35:33,730 --> 00:35:35,950
we'll definitely move to the city and buy a house there.

829
00:35:35,950 --> 00:35:36,550
This place

830
00:35:36,900 --> 00:35:39,140
feels more like an apartment for us single men.

831
00:35:39,140 --> 00:35:40,020
We can have hotpot together

832
00:35:40,020 --> 00:35:41,100
when we're free.

833
00:35:41,330 --> 00:35:42,520
There's a park nearby.

834
00:35:42,520 --> 00:35:43,750
We can get up early to exercise and walk the dog.

835
00:35:43,750 --> 00:35:44,410
No problem.

836
00:35:45,070 --> 00:35:47,870
You have even thought about your retirement life?

837
00:35:48,290 --> 00:35:49,950
I've thought about it anyway.

838
00:35:50,630 --> 00:35:52,090
We can't find a girlfriend

839
00:35:52,140 --> 00:35:53,600
with this work intensity.

840
00:35:54,100 --> 00:35:55,160
Besides, living in

841
00:35:55,170 --> 00:35:56,270
this bachelor pad

842
00:35:56,300 --> 00:35:57,960
is like living in a boy's dorm.

843
00:35:58,400 --> 00:36:00,450
We are destined to grow old together.

844
00:36:00,450 --> 00:36:01,420
I have a son.

845
00:36:02,340 --> 00:36:04,000
Who wants to grow old with you?

846
00:36:05,340 --> 00:36:06,000
Captain Lu.

847
00:36:07,540 --> 00:36:08,800
I won’t be with you too,

848
00:36:12,230 --> 00:36:14,090
Captain Lu, don't touch the wall.

849
00:36:14,990 --> 00:36:16,210
I-I-I just finished painting it.

850
00:36:16,210 --> 00:36:17,560
You don't have to remind me.

851
00:36:17,560 --> 00:36:19,420
Do you think I don't know about it?

852
00:36:24,150 --> 00:36:25,020
Those who moved in

853
00:36:25,020 --> 00:36:26,220
were all single then.

854
00:36:26,660 --> 00:36:27,170
Now,

855
00:36:27,710 --> 00:36:29,910
you're the only one who's still single.

856
00:36:31,460 --> 00:36:32,820
Please focus on the old days.

857
00:36:32,820 --> 00:36:34,620
Transferred-former-captain.

858
00:36:36,990 --> 00:36:38,060
Are you proud?

859
00:36:38,260 --> 00:36:39,420
Of course.

860
00:36:39,440 --> 00:36:40,240
What's wrong?

861
00:36:49,830 --> 00:36:50,830
I heard you were here

862
00:36:50,830 --> 00:36:52,020
before my morning training.

863
00:36:52,020 --> 00:36:54,020
So I came all the way here to meet you.

864
00:36:54,500 --> 00:36:55,360
I have to go now.

865
00:36:55,750 --> 00:36:56,230
Bye.

866
00:36:58,470 --> 00:36:59,000
So early?

867
00:37:03,620 --> 00:37:04,550
I'm not kidding.

868
00:37:05,010 --> 00:37:06,740
He can’t stay for even a minute.

869
00:37:07,230 --> 00:37:07,890
Captain Lu.

870
00:37:08,030 --> 00:37:08,510
Bye.

871
00:37:17,880 --> 00:37:18,740
Commissioner.

872
00:37:18,790 --> 00:37:19,980
SWAT Detachment of Tianwen City,

873
00:37:19,980 --> 00:37:21,040
Third Brigade, Lu Yanchen,

874
00:37:21,040 --> 00:37:22,040
reporting to you.

875
00:37:22,610 --> 00:37:23,270
Lu Yanchen.

876
00:37:23,740 --> 00:37:25,460
You must be tired from travelling all the way here.

877
00:37:25,460 --> 00:37:26,460
It’s my pleasure.

