00:37:26,480 --> 00:37:27,680
Mr. Shen was picked up

879
00:37:27,910 --> 00:37:28,850
at the station.

880
00:37:29,140 --> 00:37:29,550
Okay.

881
00:37:30,180 --> 00:37:31,300
Your Detachment Leader

882
00:37:31,300 --> 00:37:33,300
