00:37:40,690 --> 00:37:41,290
Saturday.

886
00:37:44,210 --> 00:37:45,340
I'll get going then.

887
00:37:45,690 --> 00:37:46,650
I'll go with you.

888
00:37:57,050 --> 00:37:57,450
Uncle.

889
00:38:00,220 --> 00:38:01,780
Yesterday, I heard from these old classmates of mine

890
00:38:01,780 --> 00:38:02,640
said that a hero

891
00:38:02,650 --> 00:38:03,980
will be sent back today.

892
00:38:04,820 --> 00:38:06,420
The one who sent the hero back

893
00:38:06,520 --> 00:38:07,320
is Captain Lu.

894
00:38:11,060 --> 00:38:12,320
I heard that Captain Lu

895
00:38:12,520 --> 00:38:13,980
has got married recently.

896
00:38:18,530 --> 00:38:20,260
You don't have to say anything.

897
00:38:21,410 --> 00:38:22,270
I already know.

898
00:38:25,950 --> 00:38:27,140
When did you know?

899
00:38:29,090 --> 00:38:30,220
I've already known.

900
00:38:31,910 --> 00:38:33,110
Did Gui Xiao tell you?

901
00:38:38,200 --> 00:38:40,130
When I was transferred to Gonghai,

902
00:38:40,130 --> 00:38:41,260
I have been planning

903
00:38:41,330 --> 00:38:42,460
to pay a formal visit

904
00:38:42,580 --> 00:38:43,820
with Gui Xiao

905
00:38:44,130 --> 00:38:45,790
after completing my mission.

906
00:38:49,850 --> 00:38:51,250
Since you're now married

907
00:38:52,140 --> 00:38:53,670
and have a home to go back to,

908
00:38:55,070 --> 00:38:56,520
please be careful

909
00:38:56,930 --> 00:38:58,260
when you go on a mission.

910
00:39:00,960 --> 00:39:01,360
Okay.

911
00:39:04,040 --> 00:39:04,740
Where are you going?

912
00:39:04,740 --> 00:39:06,140
I'll ask the driver to drive you.

913
00:39:06,140 --> 00:39:06,510
Home.

914
00:39:08,140 --> 00:39:08,630
OK.

915
00:39:23,100 --> 00:39:23,830
You're back.

916
00:39:26,990 --> 00:39:28,120
I came back by train.

917
00:39:28,140 --> 00:39:28,780
I'm dirty.

918
00:39:29,420 --> 00:39:30,400
I'll take a shower first.

919
00:39:30,400 --> 00:39:31,730
It's okay. I don't mind.

920
00:39:32,660 --> 00:39:33,330
I do mind.

921
00:39:34,220 --> 00:39:35,550
Are you disgusted by me?

922
00:39:36,620 --> 00:39:37,690
I disgust myself.

923
00:39:39,340 --> 00:39:39,870
Alright.

924
00:39:40,240 --> 00:39:41,500
I need to take a shower.

925
00:39:42,320 --> 00:39:43,420
Have you bought the ingredients?

926
00:39:43,420 --> 00:39:43,830
Yes.

927
00:39:43,970 --> 00:39:46,370
I bought all my favorite food ingredients.

928
00:39:50,460 --> 00:39:51,860
Why are you following me?

929
00:39:51,980 --> 00:39:53,980
I want to stay with you every second.

930
00:39:57,600 --> 00:39:58,300
Now you don't even care to greet me

931
00:39:58,300 --> 00:39:59,360
when you see me?

932
00:40:00,500 --> 00:40:01,960
It's a misunderstanding.

933
00:40:02,060 --> 00:40:02,920
I'm just trying to leave the time

934
00:40:02,920 --> 00:40:03,980
to Aunt Gui Xiao.

935
00:40:17,540 --> 00:40:19,070
I have something to tell you.

936
00:40:19,070 --> 00:40:19,560
What?

937
00:40:21,300 --> 00:40:23,210
Your mother was ill two days ago.

938
00:40:24,850 --> 00:40:26,250
But she has been discharged.

939
00:40:26,250 --> 00:40:27,400
I took care of her the whole time.

940
00:40:27,400 --> 00:40:28,130
Don't worry.

941
00:40:31,630 --> 00:40:32,540
Who called you?

942
00:40:33,320 --> 00:40:34,590
Your sister called me.

943
00:40:35,290 --> 00:40:35,890
My sister?

944
00:40:38,260 --> 00:40:39,720
I did give her your number.

945
00:40:40,420 --> 00:40:41,580
Actually, I just want her

946
00:40:41,580 --> 00:40:42,820
to have a chat with you

947
00:40:43,320 --> 00:40:45,320
and take care of you when she's free.

948
00:40:46,180 --> 00:40:47,380
You're worrying too much.

949
00:40:47,380 --> 00:40:48,100
All these years,

950
00:40:48,100 --> 00:40:49,340
I've been taking care of myself.

951
00:40:49,340 --> 00:40:50,140
It's nothing.

952
00:40:52,000 --> 00:40:53,260
You should cook later.

953
00:40:54,020 --> 00:40:54,700
No, not cooking.

954
00:40:54,700 --> 00:40:56,220
I really can't cook.

955
00:40:57,050 --> 00:40:57,910
Days without you,

956
00:40:57,910 --> 00:40:59,710
I always order food deliveries.

957
00:41:02,700 --> 00:41:04,630
How many days are you going to stay?

958
00:41:04,720 --> 00:41:05,380
Three days.

959
00:41:06,010 --> 00:41:07,140
Whole day off today.

960
00:41:07,470 --> 00:41:09,420
Tomorrow is Mr. Shen’s memorial service.

961
00:41:09,420 --> 00:41:11,620
I will go back on the day after tomorrow.

962
00:41:11,940 --> 00:41:13,470
Do you want to go back

963
00:41:14,280 --> 00:41:15,280
to visit your mom?

964
00:41:16,380 --> 00:41:17,310
I should go back.

965
00:41:17,820 --> 00:41:18,420
Together?

966
00:41:19,420 --> 00:41:19,860
No.

967
00:41:20,810 --> 00:41:22,470
We had a good chat last time.

968
00:41:24,530 --> 00:41:26,190
I don't want you to meet my dad.

969
00:41:28,660 --> 00:41:30,850
It's the same reason as yours last time.

970
00:41:30,850 --> 00:41:31,360
Why don't you

971
00:41:31,360 --> 00:41:32,820
want me to go home with you?

972
00:41:34,890 --> 00:41:36,570
I should at least say hello.

973
00:41:38,930 --> 00:41:39,630
Not now.

974
00:41:41,370 --> 00:41:42,720
We're married.

975
00:41:44,990 --> 00:41:45,790
It has nothing

976
00:41:46,130 --> 00:41:47,170
to do with them.

977
00:41:47,970 --> 00:41:48,850
I'll handle

978
00:41:49,670 --> 00:41:50,600
my own business.

979
00:41:54,030 --> 00:41:54,830
Stop staring.

980
00:41:56,100 --> 00:41:57,100
I'll cook for you.

981
00:42:05,840 --> 00:42:07,250
My skills are limited.

982
00:42:07,420 --> 00:42:08,210
I bought

983
00:42:08,210 --> 00:42:10,260
vegetables and meat that doesn't need cutting.

984
00:42:10,260 --> 00:42:11,460
You rarely come back.

985
00:42:11,560 --> 00:42:13,010
I've done everything I can

986
00:42:13,010 --> 00:42:13,940
to save you time.

987
00:42:15,450 --> 00:42:16,310
It's withered.

988
00:42:18,640 --> 00:42:20,840
Not that withered. I can make do with it.

989
00:42:22,070 --> 00:42:22,900
It seems that you are not reliable in

990
00:42:22,900 --> 00:42:24,160
buying groceries too.

991
00:42:25,600 --> 00:42:26,630
I'm being a free labor.

992
00:42:26,630 --> 00:42:28,150
Don't be picky.
